@startuml 19-ladder-a-platform-cicd
title Ladder A — Platform (AWS) CI/CD\nContent Evidence platform · ADR-010 · ADR-015 · ADR-016\nDo not conflate with Ladder B (Netlify / TTV)

left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  BorderColor #1565C0
  RoundCorner 8
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor #F9A825
}

rectangle "Developer / PR" as Dev #BBDEFB
rectangle "GitHub Actions\nlint · test · build" as GHA #90CAF9
rectangle "ECR\npush image\n[Inferred]" as ECR #FFE0B2
rectangle "Terraform\napply" as TF #A5D6A7
rectangle "ECS / Fargate\nservice update" as ECS #CE93D8

Dev --> GHA
GHA --> ECR
ECR --> TF
TF --> ECS

note bottom of GHA
  **Confirmed:** GHA CI
  (ADR-010, ADR-016)
end note

note bottom of TF
  **Confirmed:** Terraform + ECS
  (ADR-015, ADR-016)
end note

note bottom of ECS
  **Unknown:** deploy strategy
  (rolling / blue-green / canary)
  — do not invent
end note

note top of ECR
  Registry path inferred
  from container → ECS
end note

legend right
  |= Maturity |= Meaning |
  | Confirmed | GHA + Terraform + ECS (ADR-010, 015, 016) |
  | Inferred | ECR as container registry |
  | Unknown | rolling / blue-green / canary |
  | Note | Dev / Staging / Prod envs;\nidentical staging→main for platform =\nProposed / Unknown |
  | Out of scope | **No** Netlify · **No** TTV (Ladder B only) |
endlegend

@enduml
